Each Legend comes with two default weapon skins, which are equipped by default.

These weapon skins are unique in that they can only be used by the Legend they belong to. For example, [[Bödvar]] can use his default [[Warhammer]] regardless of skin equipped, but all other Hammer Legends are not able to equip it.

